title: Braun No touch + Forehead Thermometer (NTF3000) - 40s
description:
Braun No touch + forehead thermometer is the first thermometer with no touch and touch functions, gentle enough for a sleeping child. 

With its unique dual technology and ultra-sensitive sensor, now you can get fast and precise temperature readings either by touching the forehead or from a distance. You’ll also appreciate its large display with color coding, so interpreting temperature readings is easy. Enjoy the peace of mind that comes from the combination of professional accuracy and gentle convenience.
